Flask-JSUtils
=============

Flask-JSUtils is a `Flask <http://flask.pocoo.org/>`_ extension that lets you use url_for() in your javascript.

Installation
------------

pip install flask-jsutils

Usage
-----

In your application setup, with app being your flask application:

    from flask.ext.jsutils import JSUtils
    JSUtils(app)

In your template:

    {{ jsutils.js_link }}

or if you want the javascript to be rendered right inside your template 

    {{ jsutils.js_content }}

